defaultLocale.name: ColorResults
defaultLocale.description:
ColorResults is an add-on for Firefox which highlights
	the search terms from a Google search in every webpage Google has found (not in the Google results list itself).
  Usage: 1. Do a Google search. Example: 'star trek' (without the quotes).
         2. Open a link from the Google results list.
         3. Scroll the page to highlight the words 'star' and 'trek'.
defaultLocale.creator: Jochen Baier
